-- Description: Testbench for Register_Bank (8 x 4-bit registers).
--              Index 240553 -> digits: 2 4 0 5 5 3
--              Data values loaded into registers come from index digits:
--                  Reg 2 <- "0010"  (digit 2)
--                  Reg 4 <- "0100"  (digit 4)
--                  Reg 0 <- "0000"  (digit 0)  [Reg 0 is always read-only 0]
--                  Reg 5 <- "0101"  (digit 5)
--                  Reg 5 <- "0101"  (digit 5, write again same value)
--                  Reg 3 <- "0011"  (digit 3)
--              Also tests reset (all registers -> "0000") and
--              that non-selected registers hold their values.
-- 
